Util

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • Util.Node

  • public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
    Node class for shortest Path and longest Path calculations. Includes: - Node reference of the predecessor - actual Point (Position) - pathcost to this position - estimated pathcost to the target
